description:
Paddock Reporter keeps you up to date with whats happening in the world of Formula One racing.

You can ask Paddock Reporter the following:
- Who won the last race?
- When is the next race?
- What are the driver standings?
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Paddock Reporter who won the last race
name: Paddock Reporter
shortDescription: Paddock Reporter gives you Formula 1 racing results and updates.
